        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Cossura hutchingsae n. sp. Paratype, W.42865, SEM. (A) general view from dorsal side; (B) general view from lateral side; (C) anterior end, dorsal view; (D) anterior end, lateral view; (E) notochaetae of chaetiger 3; (F) neurochetae of chaetiger 6; (G) parapodia of chaetiger 25. Scale bars: A, B = 1 mm, C, D = 200 μm, E, F = 20 μm, G = 100 μm." ;
